---
import Layout from "../layouts/Main.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl prose">
      <div class="breadcrumbs text-sm mb-6">
        <ul class="flex! flex-wrap">
          <li><a href="/">Accueil</a></li>
          <li>Conditions générales</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="post">
        <h1 class="uppercase">Terms & Conditions</h1>

        <p>
          Welcome to ProCleaning. By accessing our website or using our cleaning
          services, you agree to be bound by the following Terms & Conditions.
          Please read them carefully.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h4">1. Services</h2>
        <p>
          ProCleaning provides residential and commercial cleaning services. All
          services are subject to availability and confirmation.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h4">2. Bookings</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Bookings can be made via our website, phone, or email.</li>
          <li>
            A booking is only confirmed once you receive confirmation from our
            team.
          </li>
          <li>
            We reserve the right to رفض or reschedule bookings if necessary.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="h4">3. Pricing & Payments</h2>
        <p>
          All prices are subject to change without notice. Final pricing may
          vary depending on the size, condition, and type of service required.
        </p>

        <p>
          Payment is due upon completion of service unless otherwise agreed in
          writing.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h4">4. Cancellations & Rescheduling</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Cancellations must be made at least 24 hours in advance.</li>
          <li>Late cancellations may be subject to a fee.</li>
          <li>
            We reserve the right to reschedule due to staff availability or
            emergencies.
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="h4">5. Customer Responsibilities</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Ensure access to the property at the agreed time.</li>
          <li>Secure or remove valuable and fragile items before service.</li>
          <li>Provide accurate information about the cleaning requirements.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="h4">6. Liability</h2>
        <p>
          While we take great care in providing our services, ProCleaning is not
          responsible for pre-existing damage or items not properly secured
          before cleaning.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h4">7. Service Quality</h2>
        <p>
          If you are not satisfied with our service, please contact us within 24
          hours so we can review and address your concerns.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h4">8. Website Use</h2>
        <p>
          You agree not to misuse our website, attempt unauthorized access, or
          interfere with its operation.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h4">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these Terms at any time. Continued use of our services
          means you accept the updated terms.
        </p>

        <h2 class="h4">10. Contact Information</h2>
        <p>
          For any questions regarding these Terms, please contact us:
          <br />
          <strong>Email:</strong> support@procleaning.com
          <br />
          <strong>Phone:</strong> +1 (000) 000-0000
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
